    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">子彈時間傳送。瘋狂的全螢幕Boss戰。變幻莫測的Roguelite挑戰。全球高分榜。以及合作或分割畫面戰鬥模式。這一切都發生在變幻莫測、光影絢麗的宇宙深處。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/816fc89d2a8a856411f1cea6de525465.avif?t=1768496947\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras_big/816fc89d2a8a856411f1cea6de525465.webp?t=1768496947 width=1560 height=504 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/09e07061096eb5ad4dc545ad97f78413.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>《Aluna Rift》</strong>是一款极具挑战性的街机太空射击游戏，拥有精准的操作和随机生成的类Rogue游戏模式。游戏包含单人、合作和分屏PVP模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Aluna Rift》</strong>是一款霓虹闪烁、充满怀旧气息的游戏，它向经典的街机游戏致敬，融合了现代游戏机制，并经过精心打磨，具有极高的重玩价值。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/c5beabf329b70e5979c5aeba0f4e3249.poster.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/c5beabf329b70e5979c5aeba0f4e3249.webm?t=1768496947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/c5beabf329b70e5979c5aeba0f4e3249.mp4?t=1768496947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/9b5ffd9b8e283b7aa62b278f0be16d44.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">检验您应对各种巨大敌人的能力通过在它们附近造成最大的混乱来引诱这些庞然大物，并征服随之而来的巨大挑战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/0ce679695209a6d67aa31596a06dc2e1.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/7128756b3f2f9f5218a6c13138742a7a.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">借助这一高级规避操作延缓时间对于逃离困境，进出战场，或快速移动至有用物品时非常便捷。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/4b64bf70628e83b97831707ad81c09c8.poster.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/4b64bf70628e83b97831707ad81c09c8.webm?t=1768496947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/4b64bf70628e83b97831707ad81c09c8.mp4?t=1768496947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/98a177d5e5bbbba675c722fc7a9417ae.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">与好友并肩开启一场旅程，或是与他们面对面对决 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/ef14b683dc5afa8b89364ef01da8e030.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/c58beaa619b92c42db0ba195f02a8898.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">穿越时间与空间的裂缝，搜索你的猎物。不断变化的充满活力的星系和随机出现的敌人浪潮意味着对深空的无尽探索。每次历险都各不相同。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829920/extras/50b859eb604c6ec002d9312a92596cb0.avif?t=1768496947\" width=640 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机遭遇迷你游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽生存模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级您的飞船</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球排行榜</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原声配乐 Blackout Noise</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持超宽屏幕</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck 支持</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用手柄或键盘鼠标进行游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新绑定控制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成就</p></li></ul>",
